            <characteristic name="Description" typeId="9b8f-694b-e5e-b573">While an enemy unit is within 6&quot; of this model, worsen the Leadership characteristic of models in that unit by 1. In addition, in the Battle-shock step of your opponent’s Command phase, if such an enemy unit is below its Starting Strength, it must take a Battle-shock test.</characteristic>
