                    <characteristic name="Description" typeId="9b8f-694b-e5e-b573">**^^Tyranids^^** model only. While a friendly **^^Harvester^^** model is within 12&quot; of the bearer, when using the Feed the Swarm ability, that **^^Harvester^^** model can Regenerate one friendly **^^Tyranids^^** unit that is within 9&quot; instead of one within 6&quot;.</characteristic>
