                    <characteristic name="Description" typeId="9b8f-694b-e5e-b573">**^^Tyranids Monster^^** only. If the bearer is destroyed by a melee attack, if it has not fought this phase, roll one D6: on a 3+, do not remove it from play. It can fight after the attacking model&apos;s unit has finished making its attacks, and is then removed from play.</characteristic>
