                    <characteristic name="Description" typeId="9b8f-694b-e5e-b573">**^^Tyranids^^** model only. Each time a model in the Bearer&apos;s unit makes an attack, on a Critical Wound, improve the Armour Penetration characteristic of that attack by 1.</characteristic>
                  </characteristics>
