                    <characteristic name="Description" typeId="9b8f-694b-e5e-b573">**^^Tyranids^^** model only. While the bearer is on the battlefield, each time your opponent sets up a Reserves unit on the battlefield, roll one D6: on a 2+ that unit must make a Battle-shock test.</characteristic>
