                    <characteristic name="Description" typeId="9b8f-694b-e5e-b573">**^^Vanguard Invader^^** model only. At the start of the battle, select one enemy unit. Each time the bearer makes an attack that targets that enemy unit, add 1 to the Hit roll and Wound roll.</characteristic>
