                    <characteristic name="Description" typeId="9b8f-694b-e5e-b573">**^^Trygon^^** model only. The bearer gains the **^^Synapse^^** keyword. Improve the Strength and Weapon Skill characteristics of melee weapons equipped by the bearer by 1.</characteristic>
