                  <characteristics>
                    <characteristic name="Description" typeId="9b8f-694b-e5e-b573">**^^Abominant^^**, **^^Biophagus^^** or **^^Patriarch^^** model only. Models in the bearer&apos;s unit have the Infiltrators ability and, once per battle round, you can target the bearer&apos;s unit with the Heroic Intervention Stratagem for 0CP, and can do so even if you have already targeted a different unit with that Stratagem this phase.</characteristic>
