                    <characteristic name="Description" typeId="9b8f-694b-e5e-b573">**^^Abominant^^**, **^^Biophagus^^** or **^^Patriarch^^** model only. In each Command phase, one model in the bearer&apos;s unit regains 1 lost wound.</characteristic>
