                  <characteristics>
                    <characteristic name="Description" typeId="9b8f-694b-e5e-b573">**^^Genestealer Cults^^** model only. Once per battle, when the bearer&apos;s unit declares a charge, the bearer can use the Enhancement. If it does, until the end of the phase, add 2 to Charge rolls made for the bearer&apos;s unit.</characteristic>
