                  <characteristics>
                    <characteristic name="Description" typeId="9b8f-694b-e5e-b573">Each time an attack is allocated to the bearer, subtract 1 from the Damage characteristic of that attack (note that if given to a Tyranid Prime model, this only affects that model and not other models in its unit).</characteristic>
