                  <characteristics>
                    <characteristic name="Description" typeId="9b8f-694b-e5e-b573">Once per battle, at the end of your opponent&apos;s Charge phase, the bearer can use this Enhancement. If it does, it can declare a charge as if it were your Charge phase.</characteristic>
