          <selectionEntries>
            <selectionEntry type="upgrade" import="true" name="Primary Detonator" hidden="false" id="9c6d-1f1f-45ea-fe5b">
              <profiles>
                <profile name="Primary Detonator" typeId="9cc3-6d83-4dd3-9b64" typeName="Abilities" hidden="false" id="66be-e539-7616-2db1">
                  <characteristics>
                    <characteristic name="Description" typeId="9b8f-694b-e5e-b573">Once per battle, when an enemy unit opens a closed Hatchway, if the bearer is on the battlefield, it can use this Enhancement. If it does, roll one D6: on a 3-4, that enemy unit suffers 1 mortal wound; on a 5+, that enemy unit suffers 2 mortal wounds.</characteristic>
