                  <characteristics>
                    <characteristic name="Description" typeId="9b8f-694b-e5e-b573">**^^Abominant^^** model only. Each time an enemy unit opens a Hatchway, if the bearer is within 1&quot; of that Hatchway, roll one D6: one a 3-4, that enemy unit suffers 1 mortal wound; on a 5+, that enemy unit suffers 2 mortal wounds.</characteristic>
                  </characteristics>
                </profile>
              </profiles>
