                  <characteristics>
                    <characteristic name="Description" typeId="9b8f-694b-e5e-b573">**^^Biophagus^^** model only. Each time an attack targets the bearer, subtract 1 from the Hit roll and subtract 1 from the Wound roll.</characteristic>
