    <selectionEntryGroup name="Codex Crusade Relics" id="35d6-9354-05fd-3a9e" hidden="false" collapsible="true">
      <selectionEntryGroups>
        <selectionEntryGroup name="Antiquity Relics" id="7b83-bd3a-2de2-dfc7" hidden="false" sortIndex="2">
          <selectionEntries>
            <selectionEntry type="upgrade" import="true" name="Mortrexite Implant Attack" hidden="false" id="f73f-f45a-8479-effc">
              <profiles>
                <profile name="Mortrexite Implant Attack" typeId="9cc3-6d83-4dd3-9b64" typeName="Abilities" hidden="false" id="86c1-cd9d-66fe-7125">
                  <characteristics>
                    <characteristic name="Description" typeId="9b8f-694b-e5e-b573">- Melee weapons equipped by the bearer gain the **[DEVASTATING WOUNDS]** ability.
- Each time the bearer fights, if one or more enemy models (excluding **^^Vehicle^^** models) are destroyed when resolving those attacks, after that fight is resolved you can select one friendly **^^Ripper Swarms^^** unit within 12&quot; of the bearer. If any of those destroyed enemy models had the **^^Monster^^** keyword, add D3 Ripper Swarm models to that **^^Ripper Swarms^^** unit instead.</characteristic>
                  </characteristics>
                </profile>
              </profiles>
              <constraints>
                <constraint type="max" value="1" field="selections" scope="roster" shared="true" id="a8e8-998e-d7a5-3e66" includeChildForces="true" includeChildSelections="true"/>
              </constraints>
              <modifiers>
                <modifier type="set" value="true" field="hidden">
                  <conditionGroups>
                    <conditionGroup type="or">
                      <conditionGroups>
                        <conditionGroup type="and">
                          <conditions>
                            <condition type="atLeast" value="1" field="selections" scope="roster" childId="f73f-f45a-8479-effc" shared="true" includeChildForces="true" includeChildSelections="true"/>
