                  <characteristics>
                    <characteristic name="Description" typeId="9b8f-694b-e5e-b573">Model with one or more Psychic weapons only. Each time the bearer makes an attack with a Psychic weapon, you can re-roll the Hit roll and you can re-roll the Wound roll.</characteristic>
