                  <characteristics>
                    <characteristic name="Description" typeId="9b8f-694b-e5e-b573">**^^Psyker^^** model only. Each time an enemy unit loses a wound as the result of a Psychic Attack made by the bearer:
- The bearer regains 1 lost wound.
